Package planning

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    csvfilereader
    This parses csv files meeting the official UK standard for such files at https://www.ofgem.gov.uk/sites/default/files/docs/2013/01/csvfileformatspecif(ication.pdf
    Harmonizer
    A class to optimise a set of linear production technologies to meet a Kantorovich style output target and having a pregiven set of initial resources.
    Harmony
    A class to compute the harmony function described in Towards a New Socialism
    JointProductionTechnique
    A class to represent a set of production technologies in a more compact form than as an input output table or matrix.
    nyearHarmony
    Another programme to construct 5 year or n year socialist plans
    nyearplan
    A programme to construct 5 year or n year socialist plans It produces an output file of the plan in lp-solve format on standard out
    pcsv
    class to hold csv files after they have been read in as a two D linke list
    Technique
    A class to represent a set of production technologies in a more compact form than as an input output table or matrix.
    TechnologyComplex
    A class to represent a set of production technologies in a more compact form than as an input output table or matrix.
    UKHarmony
    Another programme to construct 5 year or n year socialist plans this time it is modified to use the UK input output data as source info, ie, it handles imports and exports
    UKplan
    A programme to construct 5 year or n year socialist plans for the UK from UK statistics It produces an output file of the plan in lp-solve format on standard out
